      "content": "but what is there to rebuild? the work was everything. it wasn't just a career, it was who i was. without it, i'm just a hollow shell pretending to be a scientist. it feels like the 'me' part of my life is already dead. i'm just going through the motions of a person that doesn't exist anymore.",
